Package ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.general

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InitActivity
    Initialises the application: - Requests location, read and write and camera permissions - Initialises firebase - Computes the POIPoints - Downloads the user's data if a user is already authenticated
    MainActivity
    MainsActivity displays displays all the different pages with the ViewPager2 and the menu-bar
    SettingsMapActivity
    Activity that allows the user to select a point around which compute and download POIPoints and an elevation map for offline usage.
